<div class="overlay" style="height: 100%; background-color: rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.5);">
<div class="debatte-smallh2-datum-container"><h3 class="debatte-smallh2-datum"><time datetime="2017-08-28">28 August 2017</time></h3>                                                        <h2 class="field-content icondebatte-small debatte-smallh2-datum debatte-smallh2-datum-largeimage">Can terrorism unite Spain?</h2>
</div>
<!--
<h2 class="icondebatte-small">Can terrorism unite Spain?</h2>//-->
</div>
</a>
<div class="field-items">
<div resource="sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/field/image/imagefield_nAV21U-itok=Oc03UfMh.png" rel="og:image rdfs:seeAlso" class="field-item even">
<a href="/en/185079/can-terrorism-unite-spain" title="Can terrorism unite Spain?"><img class="swap-image" src="/cache/images/6/185086-5x3-teaser170x102.jpg?249C9" alt="Demonstrators carry banners with the slogan: &quot;We are not afraid.&quot; (© picture-alliance/dpa)" title="" typeof="foaf:Image" style="width:100%;height:auto"  data-ctrl-images='{"340":"\/cache\/images\/6\/185086-5x3-teaser340x204.jpg?ADEDF","680":"\/cache\/images\/6\/185086-5x3-teaser680x408.jpg?63C17"}'  /></a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
<div class="field-items">
<div property="content:encoded" class="field-item line-clamp even" style="word-wrap: break-word;">
<p>Ten days after the <link1>attack in Barcelona</link1> around half a million people have demonstrated against terror and violence and for solidarity. A number of people in the crowds could be heard booing King Felipe and Prime Minister Rajoy, who also attended the demonstration - provoking the ire of some commentators. Others, however, praise the Spaniards' show of unity.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
