<div class="content">
<div class="field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden">
<a href="/en/184746/can-terrorism-be-prevented" title="Can terrorism be prevented?">
<div class="overlay" style="height: 100%; background-color: rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.5);">
<div class="debatte-smallh2-datum-container"><h3 class="debatte-smallh2-datum"><time datetime="2017-08-22">22 August 2017</time></h3>                                                        <h2 class="field-content icondebatte-small debatte-smallh2-datum debatte-smallh2-datum-largeimage">Can terrorism be prevented?</h2>
</div>
<!--
<h2 class="icondebatte-small">Can terrorism be prevented?</h2>//-->
</div>
</a>
<div class="field-items">
<div resource="sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/field/image/imagefield_nAV21U-itok=Oc03UfMh.png" rel="og:image rdfs:seeAlso" class="field-item even">
<a href="/en/184746/can-terrorism-be-prevented" title="Can terrorism be prevented?"><img class="swap-image" src="/cache/images/8/184758-5x3-teaser170x102.jpg?F7AFF" alt="A woman writing &quot;peace&quot; in various languages in Barcelona. (© picture-alliance/dpa)" title="" typeof="foaf:Image" style="width:100%;height:auto"  data-ctrl-images='{"340":"\/cache\/images\/8\/184758-5x3-teaser340x204.jpg?F93E9","680":"\/cache\/images\/8\/184758-5x3-teaser680x408.jpg?FC971"}'  /></a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
<div class="field-items">
<div property="content:encoded" class="field-item line-clamp even" style="word-wrap: break-word;">
<p>After the <link1>terrorist attacks in Catalonia</link1> that left 15 people dead, security services have shot the prime suspect. Both Spain and Finland, where another attacker killed two people on Friday, are still reeling from the shock. Europe's media have very different answers to the question of how to deal with terror and whether it can be prevented at all.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</article>
</div>
<div class="col col-sm-4">
