<div class="debatte-smallh2-datum-container"><h3 class="debatte-smallh2-datum"><time datetime="2017-05-29">29 May 2017</time></h3>                                                        <h2 class="field-content icondebatte-small debatte-smallh2-datum debatte-smallh2-datum-largeimage">The fear of Islamist terror</h2>
</div>
<!--
<h2 class="icondebatte-small">The fear of Islamist terror</h2>//-->
</div>
</a>
<div class="field-items">
<div resource="sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/field/image/imagefield_nAV21U-itok=Oc03UfMh.png" rel="og:image rdfs:seeAlso" class="field-item even">
