<div class="field-items">
<div property="content:encoded" class="field-item line-clamp even" style="word-wrap: break-word;">
<p>The attack in Manchester has reignited the debate in Europe's press about how to react to Islamist terror. Can military operations put a stop to terrorism?</p>
