<div class="debatte-smallh2-datum-container"><h3 class="debatte-smallh2-datum"><time datetime="2017-04-10">10 April 2017</time></h3>                                                        <h2 class="field-content icondebatte-small debatte-smallh2-datum debatte-smallh2-datum-largeimage">Must Sweden rethink its policy of openness?</h2>
</div>
<!--
<h2 class="icondebatte-small">Must Sweden rethink its policy of openness?</h2>//-->
</div>
</a>
<div class="field-items">
<div resource="sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/field/image/imagefield_nAV21U-itok=Oc03UfMh.png" rel="og:image rdfs:seeAlso" class="field-item even">
<a href="/en/177449/must-sweden-rethink-its-policy-of-openness" title="Must Sweden rethink its policy of openness?"><img class="swap-image" src="/cache/images/1/177461-5x3-teaser170x102.jpg?D50C8" alt="(© picture-alliance/dpa)" title="" typeof="foaf:Image" style="width:100%;height:auto"  data-ctrl-images='{"340":"\/cache\/images\/1\/177461-5x3-teaser340x204.jpg?F6F8F","680":"\/cache\/images\/1\/177461-5x3-teaser680x408.jpg?2D5DC"}'  /></a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
<div class="field-items">
<div property="content:encoded" class="field-item line-clamp even" style="word-wrap: break-word;">
<p>Thousands of people demonstrated to show solidarity with the victims of Friday's truck attack on Sunday in Stockholm. The police are searching for accomplices of the suspect - an Uzbek asylum seeker who had evaded attempts to deport him. Sweden needs tighter security measures, some media outlets demand. For others, the limited scale of the attack is proof of how successful counterterrorism measures already are.</p>
</div>
