</div>
</a>
<div class="field-items">
<div resource="sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/field/image/imagefield_nAV21U-itok=Oc03UfMh.png" rel="og:image rdfs:seeAlso" class="field-item even">
<a href="/en/172088/will-terrorism-divide-turkey" title="Will terrorism divide Turkey?"><img class="swap-image" src="/cache/images/3/172103-5x3-teaser170x102.jpg?F3146" alt="(© picture-alliance/dpa)" title="" typeof="foaf:Image" style="width:100%;height:auto"  data-ctrl-images='{"340":"\/cache\/images\/3\/172103-5x3-teaser340x204.jpg?C369C","680":"\/cache\/images\/3\/172103-5x3-teaser680x408.jpg?33370"}'  /></a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
<div class="field-items">
<div property="content:encoded" class="field-item line-clamp even" style="word-wrap: break-word;">
<p>Following <link1>the attack on a nightclub</link1> in Istanbul many see Turkey's pluralist society under pressure. President Erdoğan warned in a speech about divisions in the country and promised that all citizens would retain their personal freedom. Meanwhile, hateful comments have appeared on the web criticising victims of the attack for their lifestyle. Commentators warn that the rifts in Turkish society must not be allowed to deepen.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</article>
</div>
<div class="col col-sm-4">
<article typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document" about="" class="slide-down node node-article node-promoted node-teaser b-shadow clearfix">
