<div class="content">
<div class="field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden">
<a href="/en/171928/has-erdogan-left-turkey-vulnerable-to-attacks" title="Has Erdoğan left Turkey vulnerable to attacks?">
<div class="overlay" style="height: 100%; background-color: rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.5);">
<div class="debatte-smallh2-datum-container"><h3 class="debatte-smallh2-datum"><time datetime="2017-01-03">03 January 2017</time></h3>                                                        <h2 class="field-content icondebatte-small debatte-smallh2-datum debatte-smallh2-datum-largeimage">Has Erdoğan left Turkey vulnerable to attacks?</h2>
</div>
<!--
<h2 class="icondebatte-small">Has Erdoğan left Turkey vulnerable to attacks?</h2>//-->
</div>
</a>
<div class="field-items">
<div resource="sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/field/image/imagefield_nAV21U-itok=Oc03UfMh.png" rel="og:image rdfs:seeAlso" class="field-item even">
<a href="/en/171928/has-erdogan-left-turkey-vulnerable-to-attacks" title="Has Erdoğan left Turkey vulnerable to attacks?"><img class="swap-image" src="/cache/images/7/171937-5x3-teaser170x102.jpg?03161" alt="(© picture-alliance/dpa)" title="" typeof="foaf:Image" style="width:100%;height:auto"  data-ctrl-images='{"340":"\/cache\/images\/7\/171937-5x3-teaser340x204.jpg?6EFA8","680":"\/cache\/images\/7\/171937-5x3-teaser680x408.jpg?F0CE3"}'  /></a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
<div class="field-items">
<div property="content:encoded" class="field-item line-clamp even" style="word-wrap: break-word;">
<p>The hunt for the perpetrator of the attack on a nightclub in Istanbul continues. The Turkish police have released a photo of the man suspected of killing 39 people on New Year's Eve. IS has claimed responsibility for the attack. Commentators see not just <link1>Erdoğan's Syria policy</link1> but also the wave of arrests in the aftermath of the <link2>failed coup</link2> as causes for the terrorism in Turkey.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</article>
</div>
<div class="col col-sm-4">
<article typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document" about="" class="slide-down node node-article node-promoted node-teaser b-shadow clearfix">
<span class="rdf-meta element-hidden" content="Gotteskrieger aus Europa" property="dc:title"></span><span class="rdf-meta element-hidden" datatype="xsd:integer" content="0" property="sioc:num_replies"></span>
<div class="content">
<div class="field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden">
<a href="/en/171850/deeply-wounded-by-terrorism" title="Deeply wounded by terrorism">
<div class="overlay" style="height: 100%; background-color: rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.5);">
<div class="debatte-smallh2-datum-container"><h3 class="debatte-smallh2-datum"><time datetime="2016-12-27">27 December 2016</time></h3>                                                        <h2 class="field-content icondebatte-small debatte-smallh2-datum debatte-smallh2-datum-largeimage">Deeply wounded by terrorism</h2>
</div>
<!--
<h2 class="icondebatte-small">Deeply wounded by terrorism</h2>//-->
</div>
</a>
<div class="field-items">
<div resource="sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/field/image/imagefield_nAV21U-itok=Oc03UfMh.png" rel="og:image rdfs:seeAlso" class="field-item even">
<a href="/en/171850/deeply-wounded-by-terrorism" title="Deeply wounded by terrorism"><img class="swap-image" src="/cache/images/0/171860-5x3-teaser170x102.jpg?970CE" alt="A sea of flowers and candles after the attack on a Christmas market in Berlin. (© picture-alliance/dpa)" title="" typeof="foaf:Image" style="width:100%;height:auto"  data-ctrl-images='{"340":"\/cache\/images\/0\/171860-5x3-teaser340x204.jpg?15170","680":"\/cache\/images\/0\/171860-5x3-teaser680x408.jpg?39826"}'  /></a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
<div class="field-items">
<div property="content:encoded" class="field-item line-clamp even" style="word-wrap: break-word;">
<p><link1>Brussels</link1> in the spring, <link2>Nice</link2> on the French national day, Berlin shortly before Christmas, and Turkey repeatedly: in 2016 bloody attacks shook many people in Europe leaving feelings of sorrow, powerlessness and fear in their wake. How has terrorism changed the continent and why are politicians and society apparently able to do so little to counter it?</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</article>
</div>
<div class="col col-sm-4">
<article typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document" about="" class="slide-down node node-article node-promoted node-teaser b-shadow clearfix">
<span class="rdf-meta element-hidden" content="Gotteskrieger aus Europa" property="dc:title"></span><span class="rdf-meta element-hidden" datatype="xsd:integer" content="0" property="sioc:num_replies"></span>
<div class="content">
<div class="field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden">
<a href="/en/171540/how-should-an-open-society-react-to-terror" title="How should an open society react to terror?">
<div class="overlay" style="height: 100%; background-color: rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.5);">
<div class="debatte-smallh2-datum-container"><h3 class="debatte-smallh2-datum"><time datetime="2016-12-22">22 December 2016</time></h3>                                                        <h2 class="field-content icondebatte-small debatte-smallh2-datum debatte-smallh2-datum-largeimage">How should an open society react to terror?</h2>
</div>
<!--
<h2 class="icondebatte-small">How should an open society react to terror?</h2>//-->
</div>
</a>
<div class="field-items">
<div resource="sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/field/image/imagefield_nAV21U-itok=Oc03UfMh.png" rel="og:image rdfs:seeAlso" class="field-item even">
<a href="/en/171540/how-should-an-open-society-react-to-terror" title="How should an open society react to terror?"><img class="swap-image" src="/cache/images/7/171547-5x3-teaser170x102.jpg?9915F" alt="(© picture-alliance/dpa)" title="" typeof="foaf:Image" style="width:100%;height:auto"  data-ctrl-images='{"340":"\/cache\/images\/7\/171547-5x3-teaser340x204.jpg?C5F5E","680":"\/cache\/images\/7\/171547-5x3-teaser680x408.jpg?39869"}'  /></a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
<div class="field-items">
<div property="content:encoded" class="field-item line-clamp even" style="word-wrap: break-word;">
<p>Police across Europe are searching for a Tunisian man suspected of driving a lorry into a crowded Christmas market in Berlin on Monday night. The man was known to German security agencies as an Islamist and "dangerous individual". While some journalists call for a tougher stance on Islamists, others see tolerance and openness as the only effective way of countering terrorism.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</article>
</div>
<div class="col col-sm-4">
<article typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document" about="" class="slide-down node node-article node-promoted node-teaser b-shadow clearfix">
<span class="rdf-meta element-hidden" content="Gotteskrieger aus Europa" property="dc:title"></span><span class="rdf-meta element-hidden" datatype="xsd:integer" content="0" property="sioc:num_replies"></span>
<div class="content">
<div class="field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden">
