<div class="debatte-smallh2-datum-container"><h3 class="debatte-smallh2-datum"><time datetime="2016-08-24">24 August 2016</time></h3>                                                        <h2 class="field-content icondebatte-small debatte-smallh2-datum debatte-smallh2-datum-largeimage">Kurdish wedding attack in Turkey</h2>
</div>
<!--
<h2 class="icondebatte-small">Kurdish wedding attack in Turkey</h2>//-->
</div>
</a>
<div class="field-items">
<div resource="sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/field/image/imagefield_nAV21U-itok=Oc03UfMh.png" rel="og:image rdfs:seeAlso" class="field-item even">
<a href="/en/164742/kurdish-wedding-attack-in-turkey" title="Kurdish wedding attack in Turkey"><img class="swap-image" src="/cache/images/0/164750-5x3-teaser170x102.jpg?3723A" alt="(© picture-alliance/dpa)" title="" typeof="foaf:Image" style="width:100%;height:auto"  data-ctrl-images='{"340":"\/cache\/images\/0\/164750-5x3-teaser340x204.jpg?E4CED","680":"\/cache\/images\/0\/164750-5x3-teaser680x408.jpg?37D1F"}'  /></a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
<div class="field-items">
<div property="content:encoded" class="field-item line-clamp even" style="word-wrap: break-word;">
<p>At least 51 people died in a suicide bombing at a Kurdish wedding in the south-eastern Turkish city of Gaziantep on Saturday night. The Turkish government suspects the IS was behind the attack, which according to preliminary investigation results was carried out by a boy aged between 12 and 14 years. Pinning the blame on a child is too simple, commentators write and argue that the government also bears part of the responsibility for the attack.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
