<div class="debatte-smallh2-datum-container"><h3 class="debatte-smallh2-datum"><time datetime="2016-08-04">04 August 2016</time></h3>                                                        <h2 class="field-content icondebatte-small debatte-smallh2-datum debatte-smallh2-datum-largeimage">Is Europe on the verge of religious war?</h2>
</div>
<!--
<h2 class="icondebatte-small">Is Europe on the verge of religious war?</h2>//-->
</div>
</a>
<div class="field-items">
<div resource="sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/field/image/imagefield_nAV21U-itok=Oc03UfMh.png" rel="og:image rdfs:seeAlso" class="field-item even">
<a href="/en/163309/is-europe-on-the-verge-of-religious-war" title="Is Europe on the verge of religious war?"><img class="swap-image" src="/cache/images/6/163316-5x3-teaser170x102.jpg?E20CD" alt="(© picture-alliance/dpa)" title="" typeof="foaf:Image" style="width:100%;height:auto"  data-ctrl-images='{"340":"\/cache\/images\/6\/163316-5x3-teaser340x204.jpg?EF733","680":"\/cache\/images\/6\/163316-5x3-teaser680x408.jpg?0D588"}'  /></a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
<div class="field-items">
<div property="content:encoded" class="field-item line-clamp even" style="word-wrap: break-word;">
<p>Two men forced their way into a church in Normandy last week and killed a priest celebrating mass there. The IS has claimed responsibility. The attack prompts the press to discuss the potential threat of religious war in Europe.</p>
