<div class="overlay" style="height: 100%; background-color: rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.5);">
<div class="debatte-smallh2-datum-container"><h3 class="debatte-smallh2-datum"><time datetime="2016-08-16">16 August 2016</time></h3>                                                        <h2 class="field-content icondebatte-small debatte-smallh2-datum debatte-smallh2-datum-largeimage">How should Europe counter the IS?</h2>
</div>
<!--
<h2 class="icondebatte-small">How should Europe counter the IS?</h2>//-->
</div>
</a>
<div class="field-items">
<div resource="sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/field/image/imagefield_nAV21U-itok=Oc03UfMh.png" rel="og:image rdfs:seeAlso" class="field-item even">
<a href="/en/163306/how-should-europe-counter-the-is" title="How should Europe counter the IS?"><img class="swap-image" src="/cache/images/7/163307-5x3-teaser170x102.jpg?CAD7A" alt="(© picture-alliance/dpa)" title="" typeof="foaf:Image" style="width:100%;height:auto"  data-ctrl-images='{"340":"\/cache\/images\/7\/163307-5x3-teaser340x204.jpg?80752","680":"\/cache\/images\/7\/163307-5x3-teaser680x408.jpg?D4CB2"}'  /></a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
<div class="field-items">
<div property="content:encoded" class="field-item line-clamp even" style="word-wrap: break-word;">
<p>After the most recent terrorist attacks in <link1>France</link1> and <link2>Germany</link2> the debate about how to combat the IS continues apace. Commentators focus on the radicalisation of Muslim youths and discuss how it can be prevented.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</article>
