<div class="content">
<div class="field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden">
<a href="/en/162651/france-debates-security" title="France debates security">
<div class="overlay" style="height: 100%; background-color: rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.5);">
<div class="debatte-smallh2-datum-container"><h3 class="debatte-smallh2-datum"><time datetime="2016-07-27">27 July 2016</time></h3>                                                        <h2 class="field-content icondebatte-small debatte-smallh2-datum debatte-smallh2-datum-largeimage">France debates security</h2>
</div>
<!--
<h2 class="icondebatte-small">France debates security</h2>//-->
</div>
</a>
<div class="field-items">
<div resource="sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/field/image/imagefield_nAV21U-itok=Oc03UfMh.png" rel="og:image rdfs:seeAlso" class="field-item even">
<a href="/en/162651/france-debates-security" title="France debates security"><img class="swap-image" src="/cache/images/7/162657-5x3-teaser170x102.jpg?3304E" alt="(© picture-alliance/dpa)" title="" typeof="foaf:Image" style="width:100%;height:auto"  data-ctrl-images='{"340":"\/cache\/images\/7\/162657-5x3-teaser340x204.jpg?62006","680":"\/cache\/images\/7\/162657-5x3-teaser680x408.jpg?6F9A9"}'  /></a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
<div class="field-items">
<div property="content:encoded" class="field-item line-clamp even" style="word-wrap: break-word;">
<p>France's security forces and politicians are under fire after the Nice attack in which a lorry drove into a crowd killing 84 people. What lessons must the country learn from the attack?</p>
</div>
