<div class="debatte-smallh2-datum-container"><h3 class="debatte-smallh2-datum"><time datetime="2016-07-27">27 July 2016</time></h3>                                                        <h2 class="field-content icondebatte-small debatte-smallh2-datum debatte-smallh2-datum-largeimage">Will the mood in Germany change now?</h2>
</div>
<!--
<h2 class="icondebatte-small">Will the mood in Germany change now?</h2>//-->
</div>
</a>
<div class="field-items">
<div resource="sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/field/image/imagefield_nAV21U-itok=Oc03UfMh.png" rel="og:image rdfs:seeAlso" class="field-item even">
<a href="/en/162894/will-the-mood-in-germany-change-now" title="Will the mood in Germany change now?"><img class="swap-image" src="/cache/images/8/162898-5x3-teaser170x102.jpg?5622F" alt="(© picture-alliance/dpa)" title="" typeof="foaf:Image" style="width:100%;height:auto"  data-ctrl-images='{"340":"\/cache\/images\/8\/162898-5x3-teaser340x204.jpg?6DD7E","680":"\/cache\/images\/8\/162898-5x3-teaser680x408.jpg?11B10"}'  /></a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
<div class="field-items">
<div property="content:encoded" class="field-item line-clamp even" style="word-wrap: break-word;">
<p>A Syrian man blew himself up and injured 15 others outside a music festival in Ansbach on Sunday. The authorities suspect the blast was Islamist motivated. After the axe attack in a regional train and the killing spree in Munich this latest attack has only compounded the state of shock in Germany. Commentators ask what impact all this will have on the country's attitude to refugees.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
