<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
<div class="field-items">
<div property="content:encoded" class="field-item line-clamp even" style="word-wrap: break-word;">
<p>At least eleven people were killed on Tuesday in the third major terrorist attack to hit Istanbul within the <link1>last six months</link1>. Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdoğan has blamed the PKK for the bombing but ultimately it is he who is responsible for the wave of terror in Turkey, commentators point out.</p>
